trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem"></xref> objects in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en samling av <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem"> </xref> objekter i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: The RepeaterItemCollection class represents a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem> objects, which in turn represent the data items in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen RepeaterItemCollection representerer en samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem>objekter, som representerer i sin tur dataelementene i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem>

trans-unit.source: To programmatically retrieve <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem> objects from a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> control, use one of the following methods: - Use the indexer to get a single <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem> object from the collection using array notation.
trans-unit.target: Hente programmatisk <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem>objekter fra en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater>styre, bruker du en av følgende metoder:-Bruk indekserer til å få én <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem>objektet fra samlingen matrise notasjon.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Repeater> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem>

trans-unit.source: - Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.CopyTo%2A> method to copy the contents of the collection to a <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object, which can then be used to get items from the collection.
trans-unit.target: -Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.CopyTo%2A>metode for å kopiere innholdet i samlingen til en <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>objektet, som kan brukes til å hente elementer fra samlingen.</xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.CopyTo%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.GetEnumerator%2A> method to create an <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> interface, which can then be used to get items from the collection.
trans-unit.target: -Bruk av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.GetEnumerator%2A>metode for å opprette en <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>grensesnittet som kan brukes til å hente elementer fra samlingen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.GetEnumerator%2A>

trans-unit.source: - Use `foreach` (C#) or `For Each` (Visual Basic) to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: -Bruk `foreach` (C#) eller `For Each` (Visual Basic) for å gå gjennom samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.Count%2A> property specifies the total number of items in the collection and is commonly used to determine the upper bound of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.Count%2A>egenskapen angir antall elementer i samlingen og brukes vanligvis til å finne den øvre grensen for samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection.Count%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Use this constructor to create and initialize a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection> class.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne konstruktøren til å opprette og starte en ny forekomst av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection>klassen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Collections.ArrayList"></xref> that contains the items with which to initialize the collection.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Collections.ArrayList"> </xref> som inneholder elementer som ikke i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Copies all the items from this <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection"></xref> to the specified <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object, starting at the specified index in the <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object.
trans-unit.target: Overfører alle elementene fra denne <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection"> </xref> til den angitte <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> objektet, med Start fra den angitte indeksen i den <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Use this method to copy the contents of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection> into the specified <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object, starting at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne metoden til å kopiere innholdet i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection>i den angitte <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>objektet, med Start fra den angitte indeksen.</xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > The `array` parameter must be a zero-based <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Den `array` -parameteren må være en nullbasert <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>objektet.</xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A zero-based <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> that receives the copied items from the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En nullbasert <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> som mottar kopierte elementer fra de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The first position in the specified <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> to receive the copied contents.
trans-unit.target: Den første posisjonen i den angitte <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> mottar kopierte innholdet.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem"></xref> objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter antall <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem"> </xref> objekter i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Use the Count property to determine the number of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem> objects in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: Bruk Count-egenskapen til å bestemme antall <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem>objekter i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection>samlingen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem>

trans-unit.source: The Count property is commonly used when iterating through the collection to determine the upper bound of the collection.
trans-unit.target: Count-egenskapen brukes vanligvis under gjentakelse samlingen til å finne den øvre grensen for samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The number of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataListItem"></xref> objects in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Antall <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataListItem"> </xref> objekter i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> interface that can iterate through all the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem"></xref> objects in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> grensesnitt som kan gå gjennom alle de <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItem"> </xref> objekter i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Use this method to create a <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> that can be used to iterate through each item in the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection>.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne metoden til å opprette en <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>som kan brukes til å gå gjennom hvert element i <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.RepeaterItemCollection> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property to get the item currently pointed to in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName>til å hente elementet som er angitt i samlingen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to move to the next item in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Bruk den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden til å flytte til neste element i samlingen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to move the enumerator back to the initial position.
trans-unit.target: Bruk den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden til å flytte enumeratoren tilbake til den opprinnelige plasseringen.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > After you create a <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName> object or use the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to move the enumerator to the first item in the collection, you must call the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Når du har opprettet en <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>objekt, eller bruk den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden til å flytte enumeratoren til det første elementet i samlingen du må kalle den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.MoveNext%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Reset%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the item represented by the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property is undefined.
trans-unit.target: Ellers elementet som representerer den <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen er ikke definert.</xref:System.Collections.IEnumerator.Current%2A?displayProperty=fullName>
